features: 【Superior Strength】: Our new style stainless steel cable ties are crafted from robust 304 stainless steel, excellent anti-corrosion and anti-rust performance, can play its own performance stably in various working scenarios.

【Perfect Choice】All kinds of indoor and outdoor electrical installation and industrial equipment maintenance can use our stainless steel cable ties and metal cable ties tools,these stainless steel cable ties offer a management solution for construction sites, petrochemicals, cable bundling and more.

【Easy to Use】 The stainless steel cable tie has good flexibility and is not affected by the shape of the binding object. Simply thread the tail of the cable tie into the locking position and tighten it. If you have any questions about how to use it, you can refer to our product video.

【Applications】: Whether to secure individual cables, or to bundle relevant individual cables together, cable ties are a fast and effective cable management accessory, securing objects for long periods. Ideal for cable routing, exhaust/header heat wrap, electronic engineering, automobile, home improvement, etc
